{"tid":229650,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"大哥已經死了，已經不在了！","createTime":"2017-05-04T17:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T05:13:47.000Z","uid":48791,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff70a7f62713a0862fbe2b36b2c5427038057a6","tid":229650,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/8H0u7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2F8H0u7.jpg&h=45854faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但是，他在我的背上、我的胸膛，和我一起繼續活下去！<br />\n  　<br />\n要挖洞就要一口氣突破天際！<br />\n就算是自掘墳墓也要突破障礙，突破的話就是我贏了！<br />\n你們以為我是誰啊，我是西蒙，不是卡米那大哥<br />\n我就是我！是挖洞的西蒙啊！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7d9c488beb326b5abea32e3afde0588ca630aa58","tid":229650,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/6729U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2F6729U.jpg&h=6ff3bd69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大哥 我要走了<br />\n<br />\n嗯 今次真係永別了 上吧兄弟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/tf8C2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2Ftf8C2.jpg&h=a21ae6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不會永別 永遠活在我心中"},{"pid":"4c61328a50b82cee533b7a16bbdb643f1568df72","tid":229650,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/z5S9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2Fz5S9P.jpg&h=74339ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西蒙 給我咬緊牙關!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/z0xr7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2Fz0xr7.jpg&h=3430ffee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/6qj0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2F6qj0f.jpg&h=5c2c4abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n清醒了嗎？<br />\n當你迷惘時我一定會來揍你的！<br />\n所以安心吧，有我在你身邊。<br />\n相信那個相信著你的我！！！<br />\n<br />\n嗯!"},{"pid":"48ee774db6f6c0a03cff827e80d353bfd87b838c","tid":229650,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:23:30.000Z","msg":"佢地2個最後一次 既合體 仲係第一次既GIGA DRIIL BREAK 不過........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/S0fAJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2FS0fAJ.jpg&h=a826d78a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n笑我們亂來也好無謀也好，支撐著我們的是喧嘩之路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/05432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2F05432.jpg&h=9abcf233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有牆壁阻礙就用拳頭擊碎，沒有道路就用這雙手來開創<br />\n<br />\n心中的岩漿與火焰熊熊燃燒！<br />\n<br />\n超絕合體，紅蓮螺巖！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/URdec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2FURdec.jpg&h=7272277c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/HHDsE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2FHHDsE.jpg&h=030204db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以為我！以為我們！是誰啊！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/900JP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2F900JP.jpg&h=b16716d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f33149d5ddbdd8c7f4c2c4fb4a4b574053f65bd5","tid":229650,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/hyobs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2Fhyobs.jpg&h=bd73bf10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽好，西蒙，別忘了<br />\n相信你自己，不是我相信著的你，也不是你相信著的我，相信那相信你自己的你吧！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">必殺!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/e961b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2Fe961b.gif&h=2289c7dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/4CJ2g.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2F4CJ2g.gif&h=04c28c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">GIGA</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/qb983.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2Fqb983.gif&h=b22c55b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">DRILL BREAK!!!!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/98G42.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2F98G42.gif&h=dc4c57bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/2132e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2F2132e.gif&h=05c86b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.na.cx/3R62z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.na.cx%2F3R62z.jpg&h=7d3bbe5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n別了啦 兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\